# Two-arg lambda used as accumulator.
*reduce(xs as Vec of i64, init as i64, f as (i64, i64) returns i64) returns i64
    acc is init
    i is 0
    while i < xs.length
        acc is f(acc, xs.get(i))
        i is i + 1
    acc

*main
    xs is vec()
    xs.push(1)
    xs.push(2)
    xs.push(3)
    xs.push(4)
    log reduce(xs, 0, |a, b| a + b)
    log reduce(xs, 1, |a, b| a * b)
